name: Tangle Remover
description: TropiClean Tangle Remover repels dirt, adds shine and makes brushing a breeze. This ready to use, no-rinse formula quickly penetrates mats and tangles to gently remove knots, reducing brushing time by up to 50%, allowing more time for snuggles. Our new formula delivers a revolutionary way to remove mats, tangles, undercoat, and loose hair from your pets coat. Use the Tangle Remover to cut your brushing time in half, while reviving damaged coats, restoring elasticity and leaving hair with a healthy shine. No Rinse. Brushing Made Easy.
